      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Scott Farrell</b>\n</p><p><b>Scott Farrell</b>,<br />\nan Australian consultant, chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, computer chess programmer and author of the private chess engine <a href=\"/Chompster\" title=\"Chompster\">Chompster</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, which is written in <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2002\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2002</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2003\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2003</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Farrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2002\">2002</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Farrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2002\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=247564\">I need help with Search/Selective Extension</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 24, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=253151\">MVVLVA sorting does not help for move ordering</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 21, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV-LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=267039\">new thoughts on verified null move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 23, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=267678\">pruning vs extensions vs qsearch - are these all effectively the same?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 27, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Pruning\" title=\"Pruning\">Pruning</a>, <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a>, <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=268076\">what does \"fail high\" mean?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=268121\">what does \"fail high\" mean? In the context of iterative deepening</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 30, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-High\" title=\"Fail-High\">Fail-High</a>, <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2003\">2003</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Farrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2003\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=282702\">new idea on managing time using depth reduction at root</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 08, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a>, <a href=\"/Root\" title=\"Root\">Root</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=313206\">real job of the qSearch? find quiet vs stop horizon effect</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Scott Farrell</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 28, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Horizon_Effect\" title=\"Horizon Effect\">Horizon Effect</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Farrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://auschess.org.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sepmst19.txt\">ACF Master File for September 2019</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scott_Farrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://auschess.org.au/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/sepmst19.txt\">ACF Master File for September 2019</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://computer-chess.org/doku.php?id=computer_chess:wiki:lists:private_engine_list\">Private Engine List</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://computer-chess.org/doku.php?id=home\">Computer-Chess Wiki</a> by <a href=\"/Ron_Murawski\" title=\"Ron Murawski\">Ron Murawski</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301152245\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6344-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301152245 and revision id 15312\n -->\n"
